data.description: This GORGEOUS home will check off all of your boxes, plus some! Nestled on 3.12 ACRES just outside of town, you can have country living with a short distance to the city. This home features 4 BEDROOMS, 2 BATH, plus a large FLEX space perfect for a second living area, entertainment or gaming room. CUSTOM details such as SHIPLAP and a well-designed, GOURMET KITCHEN set this home apart. Outside you will find your own oasis with an IN GROUND POOL, OUTDOOR KITCHEN and an OUTDOOR BATHROOM. There plenty of outdoor storage with a 40x36 SHOP with electricity.  Let's not forget the HOME GENERATOR! There's even more, so come see for yourself!
